**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.sample

**/.secrets
**/.secrets.*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Node / TypeScript artifacts
# ------------------------------------------------------------
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.cache/
**/coverage/
**/.nyc_output/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Rust / Soroban artifacts
# ------------------------------------------------------------
**/target/
**/.cargo/
**/.soroban/
**/.stellar/
**/.stellar-cli/

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Postman local/private files
# ------------------------------------------------------------
**/postman/*.local.postman_environment.json
**/postman/*.private.postman_environment.json

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# Temporary and runtime files
